ygData.messageBody:
Hello Folks,

I took out the 'ol fishbone ear ring tonight and did a bit of searching in OOT. The zone is HUGE, so I didnt finish before I had to quit.

The area that I searched (and found nothing but a shark guarding a lock box) is the area south of the 'sisters of erollisis' isle and 'seafury cyclops' isle all the way to the south zone border. I did not search north of these isles or west of them.

So if you drew a box with these coordinates you would get the area that I have searched:

2000, -6000
2000, -10000
-5000,-6000
-5000, -1000

Make a box out of these and that is the area that I have searched so far in OOT.

I would highly reccomend a fish bone ear ring as you are spending a LOT of time underwater.

I also searched all the water in east freeport from the docks and found nothing...

Cheers,

"FizzWizz of tunare"
